# Recent changes validation and work update no Trello

Every time some work is carried out:

- Build the project for both Android and iOS to check that the application is still functional.
- Use the Trello MCP to properly update any related card, even adding comments to them to best explain what's going on. For instance, when any change has been made, the associated Trello task card must be moved to "Doing". Then, when changes have been committed and pushed, the associated Trello task card must be moved to "Done".
